3119.title: Lenny Long Legs
3119.author: Sam Lloyd
3119.description: Here are the mini monster mates. We have already met Ernie, who likes to spot colours; and Norman, who can't resist sticking his nose in and counting all kinds of smelly things. Now meet Lenny Long-legs who likes to try out opposites.

3121.title: 301 Ways to Have Fun at Work
3121.author: Dave Hemsath
3121.description: Offers ideas culled from companies around the world for everything from funny training films to zany employee awards
